<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/41401ASSQNDLHNVKJRVQSRBSHHNBDDDQS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Michael Jackson HIStory Show";
  schema:description """
	Don’t miss your chance to see Showtime’s <span class=\"BoldText\"><span class=\"ItalicText\">The Michael Jackson HIStory Show</span></span> - returning to Canada in 2026 to commemorate 30 years since Michael Jackson’s final, ground-breaking world tour: HISTORY.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Get the full Michael Jackson concert experience with triple-threat performer Garth Field – electrifying in his role as Jackson – plus a live band, choreographed dancers, authentic costumes, state-of-the-art sound and theatrical lighting, vision and FX.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>Hear <span class=\"ItalicText\">Thriller, Billie Jean, Smooth Criminal, Bad, Beat It, ABC, Don’t Stop Til You Get Enough, Human Nature, PYT, They Don’t Really Care About Us</span> and many more performed live on stage.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>If you’ve been waiting for the concert event of the year… THIS IS IT! BOOK NOW!<span><br/></span>   <span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">*This is a tribute show and is not associated with the Estate of Michael Jackson.</span><span class=\"ItalicText\"></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $ 72.00 Adult, $ 43.00 Child age 13 & under, $67.00 Groups of 6+ <span class=\"ItalicText\">(includes GST + applicable fees)</span>
""";
