  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Prairie Moon";
  schema:description """
	Immerse yourself in the raw, poetic soundscape of <span class=\"BoldText\">Neil Young</span> with <span class=\"ItalicText\">Prairie Moon: A Neil Young Experience</span>. This powerful tribute captures the spirit of Young’s legendary career—from the haunting beauty of <span class=\"ItalicText\">“Helpless”</span> to the gritty edge of <span class=\"ItalicText\">“Rockin’ in the Free World.”</span> With soulful vocals and authentic musicianship, this show honours the depth, emotion, and influence of one of Canada’s most iconic artists. A must-see for Neil Young fans and lovers of classic rock alike.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $58.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
