<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/41001AMGNGHKLQLCLRMPJKPQBNDVJPHRD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Relive the Music 50s, 60s + 70s";
  schema:description """
	Back by popular demand – Relive the Music 50s & 60s SHOW is back after 158 standing ovations in a row across Canada with a new twist.  We are keeping the biggest hits from the 50s & 60s, plus adding 70s Disco Mania with new costumes and great entertainment like usual.  Medleys from the Disco area: to name a few – The Village People, Earth Wind & Fire, Bee Gees, Abba, Gloria Gaynor, Chic, Tramps, KC & the Sunshine Band, Sister Sledge and more 70s surprises coming. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>World champion, as seen twice on Oprah and the Ellen Show, Luisa Marshall will be performing all her magic alongside the other talented singers and the great band.   Don’t miss this show.   <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A one-of-a-kind show that takes the audience through Music History, Trivia & Memories of the 50’s & 60’s, & 70s. You will likely learn many things you never knew about these artists. You will see an energetic live band, amazing front singers, and dancers transforming and reliving three decades of music, costumes, trends, and dance, with video imagery in the background.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $69 Adult, $49 Student 18 and under <span class=\"ItalicText\">(includes GST, +applicable fees)</span>
""";
