<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/37601AJTVHGLQVMBGHJGCMHJCHGMKKBDC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Samantha Martin and Delta Sugar";
  schema:description """
	When Samantha Martin sings, you <span class=\"ItalicText\">feel</span> it.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With a voice that can shake the rafters one moment and break your heart the next, two-time Juno nominee Samantha Martin leads her award-winning band Delta Sugar with fiery conviction and soul to spare. A powerhouse in Canada’s blues and retro-soul scene, Samantha’s sound defies easy labels, melding the grit of blues, the heart of country, and the spirit of soul into something entirely her own.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From their breakout debut <span class=\"ItalicText\">Send the Nightingale</span> to their chart-topping albums <span class=\"ItalicText\">Run to Me</span> and <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Reckless One</span> (which held the #1 spot on U.S. Roots Radio for an incredible 38 weeks!) Samantha Martin & Delta Sugar have built a reputation for unforgettable live shows that move hearts and feet.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With international acclaim, multiple Maple Blues Awards, and the rare distinction of a CIMA Road Gold Award for selling over 25,000 tickets in a single year, this is a band at the top of their game. Don’t miss one of Canada’s most electrifying live acts.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $33 Member, $38 Non-Member <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-05T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
