<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/46401AJJTJHQJSQQVGTKDVGHPLJJBLHMJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "'Source Amnesia'";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">Presented by BC Movement Arts Society</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Truth vs. Fiction is explored in choreographer Joshua Beamish’s compelling work, ‘Source Amnesia’. 5 exquisite dancers navigate an ever-shifting reality in our age of misinformation and information manipulation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This 70-minute work will explore pertinent and critical themes of misinformation, fake news, memory loss, and truth in a gripping production perfectly poised for this moment in history.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“Source Amnesia moves from a quiet start into a demanding fast paced choreography. The pulsing beat accentuates the crisp movements.” </span>— Review Vancouver<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“[Beamish] has an enviable reputation for a choreographic style that emphasizes speed, clarity, and a dazzling array of body isolations” —</span> The Toronto Star<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Joshua Beamish/MOVETHECOMPANY is dedicated to the creation of innovative and engaging original dance productions. These works are created by Artistic Director, Joshua Beamish, and invited guest choreographers, both emerging and established. The company engages the public through high quality performance events and outreach activities, such as annual performance seasons, educational engagement with youth, choreographic mentorship for emerging creators and national and international touring.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>(Joshua Beamish/MOVETHECOMPANY will be launching a new company – Ballet Vancouver in its 2026/2027 season).<span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.joshuabeamish.com/movethecompany\">www.joshuabeamish.com/movethecompany</a><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.balletvancouver.com/\">www.balletvancouver.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please visit BC Movement Arts Society for more information and for our ‘Source Amnesia’ shows in Courtney and Sointula. <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.bcmovementarts.com/projects/source-amnesia\">www.bcmovementarts.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $38.00 Adult, $36.00 Senior, $34.00 Student, 14.00 Child Under 5, $31.00 Group 10+ <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-03-15T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
